org.pwr.odwa.server.metadata
Class Member

java.lang.Object
  org.pwr.odwa.server.metadata.Meta
      org.pwr.odwa.server.metadata.Member

public class Member
extends Meta

Stores internal information of a member. This class is an image of 'member' tag from metadata XML, giving a complete information set about a single member in a data warehouse project for a given level.

The information includes:

  • item - value in data base table to which this member maps
  • level - UID of level to which this member belongs
  • prevmember - UID of the previous member in member's level
  • nextmember - UID of the next member in member's level
  • dimension - UID of dimension to which this member belongs
  • hierarchy - UID of hierarchy to which this member belongs
  • children - an array of member's children UIDs

This component extends Meta class inheriting basic meta element properties from it (unique ID, name and description).
